items.title: Constructed Worlds Wiki
items.headline: Constructed Worlds Wiki
items.desc: Conworlding, also called worldbuilding, is the process of constructing an imaginary world, sometimes associated with a whole fictional universe. If you've ever wanted to create a powerful hi-tech nation or a tribe of primative warriors, then the Conworlds Wiki is for you! We don't discriminate and we welcome all!

items.name: RuneScape Wiki
items.title: RuneScape Wiki
items.headline: The RuneScape Wiki
items.desc:
Started in April of 2005, the RuneScape Wiki's goal is to remain a vast, knowledgeable source for all things in RuneScape.

The RuneScape Wiki aims to be a competitor to all major RuneScape fansites. Guides to new quests or holiday events, for example, can be made in under an hour, far ahead of other fansites.

It contains a guide to every quest and treasure trail, and over 26,000 articles about items, locations and monsters.


RuneScape is copyright 1999 - 2014 Jagex Ltd. The RuneScape Wiki is in no way affiliated with Jagex.

items.desc: WoWWiki is a wiki dedicated to cataloging the Warcraft universe (with a focus, though not priority, on World of Warcraft); covering the entire Warcraft series of games, RPG reference books, strategy guides, trading card games, comics, novels, and short stories. Get up to date on the latest World of Warcraft expansion! Look up that epic item or recipe. Share tips and tricks.

items.title: Off-world: The Blade Runner Wiki
items.desc: Off-World: The Blade Runner Wiki is dedicated to the Blade Runner novel series created by Phillip K. Dick and film series created by Ridley Scott and aims to be the best source of information related to Blade Runner and all things concerning it. This wiki is open and anyone can edit.

items.name: Narutopedia
items.title: Narutopedia
items.headline: Narutopedia, the free Naruto Wiki
items.desc: Twelve years before the start of the series, the Nine-Tails attacked Konohagakure, destroying much of the village and taking many lives. The leader of the village, the Fourth Hokage sacrificed his life to seal the Nine-Tails into a newborn, Naruto Uzumaki. Orphaned by the attack, Naruto was shunned by the villagers, who out of fear and anger, viewed him as the Nine-Tails itself. Though the Third Hokage outlawed speaking about anything related to the Nine-Tails, the children — taking their cues from their parents — inherited the same animosity towards Naruto. In his thirst to be acknowledged, Naruto vowed he would one day become the greatest Hokage the village had ever seen.

items.name: Sword of Truth Wiki
items.title: Sword of Truth Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Sword of Truth Wiki
items.desc:
Welcome to the wiki all about the Storm of Truth series of novels and the Legend of the Seeker TV series.

The Sword of Truth is a series of twelve epic fantasy novels written by Terry Goodkind. The books follow the protagonists Richard Cypher, Kahlan Amnell and Zeddicus Zu'l Zorander on their quest to defeat oppressors who seek to control the world and those who wish to unleash evil upon the world of the living...

items.name: Вукипедия

items.desc: Русская энциклопедия «Звёздных войн», которую может редактировать каждый.

items.name: Scrubs Wiki
items.title: Scrubs Wiki
items.headline: The only legit resource for Scrubs fans
items.desc:
Scrubs is an American sitcom that premiered on October 2, 2001 on NBC which aired for 9 seasons and 181 episodes. 

Fresh out of medical school, new doctors John "J.D." Dorian, his best friend Christopher Turk, and Elliot Reid start their internship at Sacred Heart Hospital. There, they meet the harsh Chief of Medicine Dr. Bob Kelso, J.D.'s reluctant mentor Dr. Perry Cox, nurse Carla Espinosa, and the deceitful and prankish Janitor. Also at the hospital are the wide range of personalities of Sacred Heart's staff, including the religious nurse Laverne Roberts, incompetent lawyer Ted Buckland, and spiteful board member Jordan Sullivan who also happens to be Cox's ex-wife. Other interns make the cut, such as the high-fiving Todd Quinlan and nervous Doug Murphy. Over the next 9 years they face personal and professional highs and lows, realizing that they can't make it through life - much less a hectic job as a doctor - on their own.

items.name: Centrum Społeczności
items.title: Centrum Społeczności
items.desc: Szukasz pomocy lub porady? Centrum Społeczności jest domem dla wszystkich użytkowników Fandomu. Dołącz do nas i poznaj innych edytorów, poznaj porady i triki itp. Znajdziesz tutaj pomocne forum społeczności, blog na temat nowości, strony pomocy oraz wielu użytkowników gotowych pomóc.

items.desc: O objetivo da RuneScape Wiki é possuir o máximo possível de fontes com qualidade acerca do RuneScape e se tornar o maior portal luso-brasileiro contendo conteúdo sobre o MMORPG mais famoso do mundo.RuneScape é marca registrada da Jagex Ltd 1999-2017. A Wiki RuneScape não é afiliada à Jagex embora esteja de acordo com seus Termos e Condições e a Política de Privacidade.

items.desc: Гарри Поттер вики – это энциклопедия обо всех персонажах, книгах, фильмах, играх и людях как-то связанных с вымышленной вселенной созданной Джоан Роулинг.

items.name: Grimorum
items.title: Grimorum
items.headline: Welcome to Grimorum, the Gargoyles Wiki
items.desc:
One thousand years ago, superstition and the sword ruled. It was a time of darkness. It was a world of fear. It was the age of gargoyles. Stone by day, warriors by night, we were betrayed by the humans we had sworn to protect, frozen in stone by a magic spell for a thousand years. Now, here in Manhattan, the spell is broken, and we live again! We are defenders of the night. We are Gargoyles!

Grimorum is a Wikia dedicated to being an exhaustive reference to the Gargoyles series as produced by Disney as well as additional Gargoyles material created and endorsed by series creator Greg Weisman.   Gargoyles is an acclaimed American animated series known for its complex story arcs and drama.

items.name: The Elder Scrolls Wiki
items.title: The Elder Scrolls Wiki
items.headline: The Elder Scrolls Wiki
items.desc: Добро пожаловать на The Elder Scrolls Wiki! Всё об играх серии "The Elder Scrolls": квесты, локации, персонажи, существа и многое другое. У нас много информации о последней игре серии - "Skyrim", одной из лучших игр 2011 года по версии большинства популярных изданий. Dawnguard, Hearthfire, Dragonborn – узнайте больше о дополнениях к великолепной игре. И, конечно, мы не забываем о предыдущих играх серии, присоединяйтесь!

items.name: Dark Runescape Wiki
items.title: Dark Runescape Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Dark Runescape Wikia
items.desc: Rule 8 prohibits multiple account logging-in and interaction between RuneScape accounts, including Drop Trading. It is one of the Rules of Conduct. In short, players who own multiple accounts cannot transfer items between their accounts in any way, including logging into two accounts at the same time (on one computer or two computers) and trading between them. This is a very difficult rule to be able to report, as there is no true way to know whether or not the player is using multiple accounts. If a player violates Rule 8, the accounts that interacted with each other will receive a temporary or permanent ban.

items.name: Naruto Fanon Wiki
items.title: Naruto Fanon Wiki
items.headline: Naruto Fanon Wiki
items.desc: Naruto Fanon Wiki is undoubtedly dedicated to fanon/fanfiction about Naruto, the popular manga and anime series. In their own words, Naruto Fanon Wiki strives to become the preeminent and largest Naruto Fanon fanbase in the world and has over 25000 pages worth of content that readers of the series would enjoy.

items.name: Shadowrun Wiki
items.title: Shadowrun Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Shadowrun Wiki!
items.desc: Shadowrun is a role-playing game set in a fictional alternate universe. Shadowrun combines cyberpunk and high fantasy to create a near future world where technology has advanced beyond our understanding, powerful mega corporations control everyday life, and magic and classical fantasy races have returned to the world.

items.name: WoWWiki
items.title: WoWWiki
items.headline: Вселенная World of Warcraft
items.desc: Вики о знаменитой серии MMORPG World of Warcraft. Также здесь можно найти информацию о классических играх мира военного ремесла: Warcraft I, II и III. Информация собирается с различных источников в интернете в одно место. Например, на странице об Архимонде можно найти не только его характеристики или биографию, а также информацию о родственниках, исторических местонахождениях, изображения из игры или различные фан-арт рисунки, цитаты из игры и тактики боев с его участием.

items.name: Вики Сообщества
items.title: Вики Сообщества
items.desc: ФЭНДОМ — это место, где Вы можете создать вики-сообщество на любую тему или коллективно работать над развитием уже существующих проектов.  На Вики Сообщества можно узнать подробнее о различных википроектах русскоязычного портала ФЭНДОМА, узнать новости всего сообщества ФЭНДОМА, получить помощь и советы от опытных участников.

items.name: RuneScape Fan Fiction Wiki
items.title: RuneScape Fan Fiction Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the RuneScape Fan Fiction Wiki
items.desc:
RuneScape is a fantasy massively multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG).  It takes place in the world of Gielinor, a medieval fantasy realm divided into different kingdoms, regions, and cities. Players can travel throughout Gielinor via a number of methods including on foot, magical spells, or charter ships. Each region offers different types of monsters, resources, and quests to challenge players.

This wiki is a place for all to share their own RuneScape fan fictions.

items.name: Scrubs-Wiki
items.title: Scrubs-Wiki
items.headline: Scrubs - Die Anfänger
items.desc: Schau doch mal im Scrubs-Wiki vorbei und erlebe hautnah und in allen Einzelheiten, was in den 9 Staffeln von Scrubs geschah. Hier erfährst du alles über J.D. & seine Kollegen, die gesamten Folgen und welche davon als nächstes im Fernsehen ausgestrahlt werden. UND: Mit über 1.600 Seiten sind wir das größte Scrubs-Wiki weltweit. Also, lass dich überraschen und schau vorbei: wir würden uns freuen!

items.name: Gyaru Wiki
items.title: Gyaru Wiki

items.desc: The Gyaru Wiki was created in the hope of spreading info about the wonderful gyaru lifestyle to all over the world. It strives to be a comprehensive encyclopedia about known gyaru (a girly-glam style), gyaru magazines, music, the gyaru-o, and more! Enter to learn more and to contribute anything you might know about the gyaru lifestyle!

items.name: Naruto Wiki
items.title: Naruto Wiki

items.desc: Naruto Wiki es una enciclopedia virtual dedicada a la recolección y organización de información sobre la serie Naruto. Aquí encontraras todo sobre el emocionante franquicia: personajes, jutsus, aldeas, manga, anime y explorar el gran mundo ninja de la mano de sus protagonistas, además ¡tú puedes ayudarnos a crecer siendo editor!

items.name: Faerûnpedia
items.title: Faerûnpedia
items.headline: Willkommen in der Faerûnpedia
items.desc: Faerûnpedia ist ein Projekt zum Aufbau einer umfassenden Forgotten Realms-Datenbank auf Basis von MediaWiki. Dadurch ist es möglich, dass alle Besucher an dieser Seite arbeiten können. Der Name Faerûnpedia setzt sich aus dem Begriff Faerûn, dem größten und wichtigsten Kontinent der Vergessenen Reiche, und dem englischen Wort für Enzyklopädie zusammen.

items.name: RuneScape Wiki
items.title: RuneScape Wiki
items.headline: RuneScape Wiki
items.desc: RuneScape ist ein MMORPG. Die Handlung des Spiels ist in einer mittelalterlich anmutenden Fantasywelt angesiedelt. Die kostenlose Version von RuneScape wird von über zehn Millionen Spielern gespielt, es bestehen zudem rund eine Million kostenpflichtige Konten. Da viele Spieler mehrere Konten besitzen, ist die exakte Anzahl der Spieler unbekannt. RuneScape gehört damit zu den bevölkerungsreichsten Online-Spielen der Welt.

items.name: Gruntipedia
items.title: Gruntipedia
items.headline: Gruntipedia, Halo humor!
items.desc:
Gruntipedia is the Halo humor wiki, featuring comedic retellings of the events of the Halo series, and some new stories, such as the life of the Prophet of Haters, Meat and Taters, the Great Covenant Book of Jokes, Kwarsh the Grunt king, the the energy known as "Gruntiness" and many more!


If you love Halo or Uncyclopedia, you'll love this!

items.name: Fruits Basket Wiki
items.title: Fruits Basket Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Fruits Basket Wiki and Database!
items.desc: Fruits Basket (sometimes abbreviated Furuba) is a Japanese manga series by Natsuki Takaya. It was serialized in the semi-monthly Japanese magazine Hana to Yume, published by Hakusensha, from 1999 to 2006. The series was also adapted into a 26-episode anime series, directed by Akitaro Daichi. The series tells the story of Tohru Honda, an orphan girl who, after meeting Yuki, Kyo, and Shigure Sohma, learns that thirteen members of the Sohma family are possessed by the animals of the Chinese zodiac and are cursed to turn into their animal forms if they embrace anyone of the opposite sex. The name was derived from a popular children's game, called Fruits Basket.

items.name: Urusei Yatsura Wiki
items.title: Urusei Yatsura Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Urusei Yatsura Wiki!
items.desc: Hello and welcome to the Urusei Yatsura Wikia, the informative database for the manga and anime Urusei Yatsura that anyone can edit! Please feel free to contribute to our site and help us make this the most informative site for everything related to the Urusei Yatsura universe created by the one and only "Princess of Manga", Rumiko Takahashi! 295 articles and counting!

items.name: Rule of Rose Wiki
items.title: Rule of Rose Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Rule of Rose Wiki!
items.desc:
Rule of Rose is a survival horror game for the PlayStation 2 developed by Punchline and published by Atlus in 2006. It has often been compared with other similar survival horror gaming series such as Silent Hill and Clock Tower, due to the psychological horror elements used throughout, and its distorted storyline. It is also compared to the one-shot game, Haunting Ground due to the use of a canine companion for the main character.
Set in 1930, Cardington, Bedfordshire, England, a few years before the second World War broke out, the game tells the story of a teenage girl named Jennifer as she is forced to work for the Red Crayon Aristocrat Club: an unruly, cruel society formed by the children of the Rose Garden Orphanage.

items.name: Naruto Wiki
items.title: Naruto Wiki
items.headline: Witaj na Naruto Wiki
items.desc: Naruto Wiki to wiki o mandze, anime, filmach, grach i bohaterach serii Masashiego Kishimoto - Naruto oraz o jego marzeniu zostania przywódcą wioski - Hokage. Na drodze młodego shinobi istnieje wiele przeszkód, w tym Czwarta Wielka Wojna Shinobi oraz dwie potężne postacie. Poznaj losy bohaterów tej wspaniałej mangi i pomóż im stawić czoła przeciwnością losu, jakie ich spotykają, jesteś na to gotów KUMALSKI ?!

items.name: Tractor & Construction Plant Wiki
items.title: Tractor & Construction Plant Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Tractor & Construction Plant Wiki
items.desc:
The Wiki (Encyclopedia) about Tractors And Construction Plant that anyone can edit. For collecting of information about the History of all makes and models manufactured and sold or imported in the world. The collecting and preservation of machines in the UK

Basically anything Tractor or Plant related, from the Earliest Steam Engines & Steam Shovels to the latest 500 hp Quadtrac type Tractors. Plant from Giant Electric Face Shovels or just a Micro Digger. Also covers the Heavy Haulage Trucks and machinery to transport equipment about and the earlier trucks, with Stationary Engines & Agricultural Implements as well.

For Collectors or just the Interested including Collections, Shows, Clubs, Owners Groups, Scale Models, Etc.

Lo scopo di questo sito è quello di tenere tutti i fan di Naruto sempre informati su cambiamenti che avvengono nelle cinque grandi terre dei ninja. Se ritenete di sapere tutto su Naruto, dimostratelo contribuendo alla wiki!

items.name: RuneScape Clans Wiki

items.desc: Welcome to the Runescape Clans Wikia! Runescape Clans Wikia is based entirely on clans from the MMORPG game RuneScape. The RuneScape Clans Wiki's goal is to become the number one source for everything related to RuneScape Clans. It is a database that includes articles about clan features, leadership, types of clans and organizations, alliances, clan pages, and clan tactics. Enter now to learn more about Runescape clans!

Wir begleiten den jungen Naruto Uzumaki aus Konohagakure, der es sich zum Ziel gemacht hat, ein Hokage, der oberste Ninja seines Dorfes, zu werden.

items.name: Quondam et Futurus

items.headline: Quondam Et Futurus- welcome to the great King Arthur Wiki!
items.desc: The Once and Future Wiki is the place to discuss and learn about over a thousand years worth of representations of King Arthur and the Knights of the Round table. We seek to be as comprehensive as possible, from ancient Welsh legends and Medieval romances, to Victorian poetry and modern television and films.

items.name: MeerUndMehr - Fanfiction Writing Wiki

items.name: Rugrats Wiki
items.title: Rugrats Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Rugrats Wiki
items.desc: Rugrats is an animated television series created by Arlene Klasky, Gábor Csupó, and Paul Germain for Nickelodeon. The series premiered on August 11, 1991 and aired its last episode on June 8, 2004. The series focuses on six babies, mainly Tommy Pickles, Tommy's mean three-year-old cousin, Angelica, and the Pickles' family dog, Spike. The show was cancelled recently, but is still playing in reruns on Nickelodeon and NickToons.

items.desc: Ce wiki traite de tout ce qui concerne l'univers de Naruto et du monde ninja.

items.desc: Divinipedia is a collaborative encylopedia about the Kid Icarus video game franchise. The storyline has elements from Greek mythology and features Pit as the protagonist, who can "jump like Mario, collect items like Link, and shoot things like Samus." This wiki contains information about gameplay, plotlines, characters, and related paraphernalia.

items.name: Big Brother UK Wiki
items.title: Big Brother UK Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Big Brother UK Wiki!
items.desc: Big Brother UK Wiki is a wiki which contains information about the reality TV show Big Brother UK, which aired from 2000 – 2010 on Channel 4 and from 2011 onwards on Channel 5. We are hoping that this wiki continues to be a very worthwhile encyclopedia of Big Brother UK information, and we really need your help to make it happen. So go on! If you can think of a relevant article to create on this wiki, fire away!

items.name: Rurouni Kenshin Wiki
items.title: Rurouni Kenshin Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Rurouni Kenshin Wiki!
items.desc:
Rurouni Kenshin Wiki is a collaborative website about the series: Rurouni Kenshin: Meiji Swordsman Romantic Story (るろうに剣心 明治剣客浪漫譚, Rurōni Kenshin Meiji Kenkaku Rōmantan), also known as Rurouni Kenshin and Samurai X. It is a Japanese manga series written and illustrated by Nobuhiro Watsuki.

we are a resource for all fans to track the characters, storylines, and battles of this epic story.

items.name: Runaways Wiki
items.title: Runaways Wiki
items.desc: Every teenager thinks their parents are evil. But what if they really were? When six L.A. teens stumble onto a terrible secret, they realize their parents have been lying to them all their lives. But what are their parents after? And why? While the kids investigate, the adults start to wonder if their kids are hiding secrets of their own. The parents close in on the truth just as the kids uncover a plan with devastating consequences. Now, this unlikely crew of teenagers must band together to stop their parents before it’s too late.

items.name: Runes of Magic Wiki
items.title: Runes of Magic Wiki

items.desc: Herzlich Willkommen im Runes of Magic-Wiki! Auf bisher schon über 1800 Artikeln sammeln wir alle Informationen rund um das Online-Rollenspiel Runes of Magic! Es gibt immer etwas zu tun, wenn du dich beteiligen möchtest, schau dir doch mal einfach mal die Stubs oder die gewünschten Seiten an.

items.name: Аватар Вики
items.title: Аватар Вики
items.headline: Добро пожаловать на Аватар Вики!
items.desc: Присоединяйтесь к приключениям Аанга, Корры и их друзей в замечательном и уникальном мире Аватара, в котором живут маги, необычные животные и загадочные духи. Люди разделены на четыре нации: Племя Воды, Царство Земли, Народ Огня и Воздушных кочевников. Представители каждой нации могут покорить только свой стихийный элемент, но магический дар проявляется не у всех. Единственным человеком, который может управлять всеми стихиями, является Аватар. На протяжении многих веков Аватар хранит равновесие в мире, выступает посредником между миром людей и миром Духов и решает сложные проблемы, затрагивающие все нации.

items.name: Tales Runner Wiki
items.title: Tales Runner Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Tales Runner wiki!
items.desc:
This wiki is dedicated to US Official Release of the Tales Runner game, published by Gala-Net under theirgPotato trademark.

Tales Runner is an online multiplayer racing game developed by South Korean company Rhaon Entertainment and originally published by Nowcom.

US Tales Runner is published by Gala-Net, a subsidiary of Japan company Gala.

Tales Runner is an athletic racing game - players are operating characters using various equipments running, jumping, swimming, or skiing in various racing maps in several racing modes (single, team, survival, relay). Racing maps are themed around various stories, either taken from famous tales (such as Jack and Beanstalk), or created by game developers as a background story for the game development.

items.name: Grand Theft Wiki
items.title: Grand Theft Wiki
items.headline: Приветствуем Вас на энциклопедии игр серии Grand Theft Auto!
items.desc: Добро пожаловать на русскоязычную энциклопедию игр серии игр Grand Theft Auto компании Rockstar Games, которую может редактировать каждый! Мы пишем о серии GTA и обо всём, связанном с серией GTA. Коротко о серии.Игры предлагают игроку роль преступника (обычно имеющего статус «шестёрки») в большом городе, продвигающегося с развитием сюжета по карьерной лестнице организованной преступности. Главари преступного мира дают игроку различные поручения (задания, миссии), которые нужно выполнять для продвижения по сюжету. По большей части это ограбления банков, заказные убийства и другие преступные действия. Также в качестве альтернативного времяпрепровождения доступно зарабатывание денег на такси; работа пожарным, полицейским, водителем машины скорой помощи, курьером; сутенерство; стрит-рейсинг; обучение управлению летательными средствами. Эти необязательные для выполнения задания доступны в перерывах между сюжетными миссиями.Мы ждём Вас! Мы всегда будет рады Вам!

items.headline: Welcome to the School Rumble Wikia!
items.desc: School Rumble (スクールランブル, Sukūru Ramburu) is a Japanese manga series written and illustrated by Jin Kobayashi and serialized in Weekly Shōnen Magazine.The final chapter was released on July 23, 2008, and the 283 chapters were collected in 22 bound volumes by Kodansha. The sequel, School Rumble Z, is now published in the monthly Shōnen Magazine Special as well, but the first two chapters (as of late October) have been short, one chapter stories.

items.title: Naruto OC Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to The Naruto Originals Wikia!
items.desc:
Welcome to the Naruto Originals Wiki (N.O.W. to the cool kids), a webspace devoted to cataloguing good original characters in the Naruto fandom, where only the top roleplayers, fanfiction writers, and fanartists on the internet are listed. This site was originally developed by fellow creator and avid supporter of OCs allismine in January 2009.
There's no sugar-coating it, people. The significant majority of original characters in this fandom (or any fandom) are flat-out Mary Sues. What we are trying to do here is reduce the discrimination and stereotyping the OC-inclusion genre faces on a regular basis by proving not all OCs suck.

Oh, yeah. I can imagine how hard it is for some of you to read that last line and not call shenanigans. Trust me, they exist. This wiki is determined to prove it.

For creators. Having your original character accepted as a page on this site would deem you and your esteemed creation the cream of the proverbial crop. As with the permissions of any wikia, you are given free creative reign to upload pictures, data, and links related to your OC on their page at any time; as this wiki grows in size, the reputability and popularity of those who have pages, deemed best of the best, are available for the world to see.
For working and prospective writers. Still working on your character? No fear! Creating a test article on your user page is the perfect opportunity for you to put your character into perspective by sketching out his / her entire plotline and purpose within the story, and also to feather out / develop your character(s) further, giving the general public, moderators, and sysop alike a chance to provide critique on your talk pages; the latter gives the creator the opportunity to
For readers. The skeptics, the supporters, the sporkers; anyone looking for a good OC story to read would simply have to browse around for something that catches their eye, ensured that nothing which is posted here isn't quality.
